{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_01","textHome":"我家的中华料理店，从父辈开始就快倒了……@可母亲和奶奶依旧每日挥霍无度……@但是，面对这样一家子总要有人能担起责任！@那么，我，由比鹤乃！@总有一天会成为成大事立大业的人！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_18","textHome":"好，完成了！右腿单立保持了24小时！@好漫长啊……说来，这个训练比起消耗体力，@更像是在与无聊做斗争啊。@不过，左腿也来练一下吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":201,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_19","textHome":"还不够还不够还不够！……我还要变的更强！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":101}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":100300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_1003_00_20","textHome":"嗯嗯，这样确实上了一个台阶！肯定没错！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_